    "body": "- Change maintainer\r\n- Change gearshifft version\r\n- Add patch to rename CMake variable that already exists in newer CMake\r\n  versions\r\n- Take renamed CMake variables for different backends into account\r\n  (`-DGEARSHIFFT_BACKEND_*`)\r\n- Only use GEARSHIFFT_BACKEND_FFTW_PTHREADS if ~openmp\r\n- Explicitly disable float16 support\r\n- Use correct minimum required Boost version\r\n- Add variants for Intel MKL and ROCm rocfft\r\n\r\nCC: @psteinb @ax3l @haampie @h-denpo @tldahlgren \r\n\r\nMy follow-up to #21437. Installing `gearshifft~cufft~clfft~rocfft~mkl+openmp` and `gearshifft~cufft~clfft~rocfft~mkl~openmp` seems to work fine. The other variants were not tested, yet.",
